OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBig Issue: Former magazine 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fvendor now runs successful 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffashion firm               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former Big Issue vendor in London who
OL,6, now runs his own multi-million pound   
OL,7, sustainable fashion firm has spoken    
OL,8, about how his time selling the magazine
OL,9, helped him start his business.         
OL,11,FPhilip Waltham sold the magazine for   
OL,12,Fthree years in Clerkenwell and         
OL,13,FHampstead in London.                   
OL,15,FHe said he ran away from home in Hull  
OL,16,Fas a teen to escape his drug addiction.
OL,18,FThe 44-year-old said the Big Issue     
OL,19,Fhelped "put money in my back pocket and
OL,20,Ffeed myself".                          
